-36318","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-wisdom-al-hikmah","tag-death-mawt","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-parables-amthal","tag-son-of-adam-ibn-adam","tag-worldly-hopes-al-aml","tag-worldly-life-dunya"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9rM","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":36321,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/25\/hopes-exceed-lifespan\/","url_meta":{"origin":36318,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Aml: Your worldly hopes exceed your lifespan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo you know what these are?\u201d The Prophet threw down two pebbles. They said, \u201cAllah and His Messenger know best.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThis further one is your worldly hope and this closer one is your lifespan.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6834,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/eating-third-food-drink-air\/","url_meta":{"origin":36318,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Eating: Filling stomach a third for food, drink, air","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miqdam ibn Ma\u2019dikarib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe son of Adam cannot fill a vessel worse than\u00a0his stomach, as\u00a0it is enough\u00a0for him to take a few bites to straighten his back. If he cannot do it, then he may fill it with\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13984,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/05\/anger-coal-lie-down\/","url_meta":{"origin":36318,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Anger: Son of Adam\u2019s anger is a hot coal, let him lie down","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, anger is a burning ember in the heart of the son of Adam, as you see it in the redness of his eyes and the bulging of his veins. Whoever feels anything like that,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40400,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/05\/takathur-misleads-you\/","url_meta":{"origin":36318,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Takathur: Competition for worldly goods misleads you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Zubayr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf the son of Adam had two valleys full of wealth, he would desire a third. Nothing satisfies his belly but the dust of the grave, yet Allah relents to those who repent.\u201d Ubayy said, \u201cWe\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38541,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/25\/iblees-snout\/","url_meta":{"origin":36318,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Satan: Shaytan withdraws when Allah is remembered","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 25, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu'adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, Satan has a snout like that of a dog positioned over the son of Adam, reminding him of his lusts and his pleasures, bringing him vain hopes and bringing his whisperings to incite doubt\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18070,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/06\/cannot-escape-trials-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":36318,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Worldly Hopes: Man cannot escape trials of life","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 6, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, drew a square, and in the middle he drew a line which poked out the end. Across the middle line, he drew some smaller lines. The Prophet said, \u201cThis is man and the square surrounding him is death.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36318","targetHints":